{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"34":"Clothing (Kitab Al-Libas)"},"section_detail":{"34":{"hadithnumber_first":4020,"hadithnumber_last":4158,"arabicnumber_first":4020,"arabicnumber_last":4158}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":4075,"arabicnumber":4075,"text":"Rapporté par Jabir ibn Abdullah رضي الله عنه : Quand je suis venu voir le Prophète ﷺ, il était assis, les mains autour des genoux, portant un manteau dont la bordure recouvrait ses pieds","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":34,"hadith":56}}]}